{"id":526028074,"lang":"cpp","time":"4Â months","timestamp":1626874622,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"380 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/526028074/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Trapping Rain Water","memory":"14.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int trap(vector<int>& height) {\n        int ans = 0;\n        \n        for(int i=0;i<height.size();i++){\n            int lmax = 0;\n            int rmax = 0;\n            for(int j=0;j<=i;j++)\n            {\n                lmax = max(lmax,height[j]);\n            }\n            for(int j=i;j<height.size();j++)\n            {\n                rmax = max(rmax,height[j]);\n            }\n            ans = ans+min(lmax,rmax)-height[i];\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"trapping-rain-water"}
